commitResults.messageTitle: Refactor Person class into Expense class (#40)
commitResults.messageBody:
* Rename package model.person to model.expense

* Rename Name class to Description class

* Rename 'name' in fields and methods containing the word with 'description'

* Rename class expense.Phone to expense.Price

* Rename Person class to Expense class

Note: caused regression in reading json files

* Rename all instances of classes with Person to Expense

* Hide Email and Address from ExpenseListCard

* Change CLI prefix for DESCRIPTION parameter

* Comment out Address and Email classes and their usage

* Remove Address and Email classs

Note: Need to fix test cases

* Change input constraints for Price

Change GUI to show price more clearly

* Fix test classes regressions and checkstyle issues caused by refactoring
